==English==

===Adjective===
'''Ruthian'''
# {{baseball}} A prodigious batting accomplishment, typically describing the flight of a long home run.  From the name of Babe Ruth.
#: ''Jones launches a '''Ruthian''' blast; it lands high in the upper deck.''
# A prodigious accomplishment
#: ''Widgets, Inc. turned in a '''Ruthian''' quarter; their stock jumped 43% the next day as a result.''